<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reserva Confirmada | <%= empresa.nombre %></title>
    <meta name="description" content="Tu reserva ha sido recibida." />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/website.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50">

    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <main class="container py-12 md:py-24">
        <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto bg-white p-8 md:p-12 rounded-lg shadow-lg text-center">
            
            <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-green-500 mx-auto" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>

            <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-4">Â¡Reserva Recibida!</h1>
            
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mt-4">
                Hemos recibido tu solicitud de reserva. Nos pondremos en contacto contigo a la brevedad
                para confirmar los detalles y coordinar el pago del abono.
            </p>

            <% if (reserva) { %>
                <div class="mt-6 border-t pt-6 text-left space-y-2">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">Detalles de tu Solicitud:</h3>
                    <div class="flex justify-between">
                        <span class="text-gray-600">ID de Reserva:</span>
                        <span class="font-medium font-mono text-sm"><%= reserva.id %></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex justify-between">
                        <span class="text-gray-600">Llegada:</span>
                        <span class="font-medium"><%= new Date(reserva.fechaLlegada + 'T00:00:00-03:00').toLocaleDateString('es-CL', { day: '2-digit', month: 'short' }) %></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex justify-between">
                        <span class="text-gray-600">Salida:</span>
                        <span class="font-medium"><%= new Date(reserva.fechaSalida + 'T00:00:00-03:00').toLocaleDateString('es-CL', { day: '2-digit', month: 'short' }) %></span>
                    </div>
                     <div class="flex justify-between">
                        <span class="text-gray-600">Total:</span>
                        <span class="font-medium">$<%= reserva.precioFinal.toLocaleString('es-CL') %></span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            <% } %>

            <div class="mt-8">
                <a href="/" class="btn">Volver al Inicio</a>
            </div>

        </div>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>